Package com.stasroshchenko.diploma.request.visit

Class CreateVisitRequest

java.lang.Object
com.stasroshchenko.diploma.request.visit.CreateVisitRequest
public class CreateVisitRequest extends Object
Create visit - the doctor user has a data about non registered user, that needs in an appointment with this specialist and creates VisitStatus.ACTIVE visit. -> ACTIVE Made for both encapsulating all doctor user's 'create' visit data, entered in 'create' visit form and sending this data as one object to controller. Some fields have validation constraints.
Version:
1.0
Author:
staffsterr2000
See Also:
Visit, VisitStatus
